text: Typhoon Matmo (also Typhoon Henry) was a tropical cyclone. The storm struck Taiwan in July 2014. The storm also hit eastern China. Damage totaled $567 million. Sixty-two people died from the typhoon. Matmo Category:2014 disasters Category:2014 in weather Matmo Category:July 2014 events Category:2010s in Taiwan Category:2014 in China
